Travel Booking Platform Using Agile
1. Introduction

A Travel Booking Platform allows users to book flights, hotels, and travel packages online. It simplifies travel planning by providing all services in one platform.

2. Objectives

To provide online booking services

To manage travel packages

To improve user convenience

3. Scope

The system enables users to search destinations, book tickets, and manage reservations.

4. Agile Methodology

The platform is developed in multiple sprints. Each sprint delivers features like booking, payment, and user profile management.

5. Key Features

User registration and login

Search and booking system

Payment processing

Booking history

6. Advantages

User-friendly interface

Fast booking process

Easy updates

7. Conclusion

Using Agile methodology helps in building a flexible and scalable travel booking platform.
